## mySASS ADVANCED

MASSIVE SASS STARTER PACK. THIS PACK WAS BUILD USING THE 7-1 FILE ARCHITECTURE 
FOR MODERN  AND EASY IN MAINTENANCE FILE SYSTEMATIC.
I AM HIGHLY RECOMMENDING READING AND USING THE SASS
GUIDELINES:

###### INTERNATIONAL VERSION
https://sass-guidelin.es/
###### GERMAN VERSION 
https://sass-guidelin.es/de/

